	the percentage changes of the Basket from the Starting Value to the Ending Value. The Basket Stocks are described in the section
	“The Basket Stocks” below. Each Basket Stock was assigned an initial weight on the pricing date, as set forth in the
	table below.


	 


	For more information on the calculation of the value of the
	Basket, please see the section entitled “Description of the Notes—Basket Market Measures” beginning on page PS-26
	of product supplement STOCK STR-1.


	 


